00:27:11.115 --> 00:27:12.240
DAVID FERRIERO: Facsimiles.

00:27:12.240 --> 00:27:13.698
SARA STEFANI:
Facsimiles, for sure.

00:27:13.698 --> 00:27:15.480
For sure.

00:27:15.480 --> 00:27:17.130
But I thought this was a great--

00:27:17.130 --> 00:27:19.080
that these letters
