00:27:28.740 --> 00:27:31.620
It is not just for
Presidential Records

00:27:31.620 --> 00:27:34.290
and of course, it is for that.

00:27:34.290 --> 00:27:36.780
But we're all in
it, essentially.

00:27:36.780 --> 00:27:39.492
DAVID FERRIERO: One of the
activities for the sleepover

00:27:39.492 --> 00:27:40.950
